Ext.data.JsonP['PyDev_Rename_Occurrences']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>PyDev Rename Occurrences</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083060\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>PyDev Rename Occurrences</h1>\n    <p>The rename occurrences feature enables you to rename all the occurrences of some token in a file.    </p>\n    <p><strong class=\" \">KEYBINDING:</strong> Ctrl+2+R    </p>\n    <p>    <img src=\"images/pydev.org/images/renameoccurrences/renameoccurrences.png\" alt=\"images/pydev.org/images/renameoccurrences/renameoccurrences.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-external-resource confluence-content-image-border\">\n        </img></p>\n    <p>Image showing the rename in action    </p>\n    <p>Note that you can iterate through the occurrences with <strong class=\" \">Tab</strong> and finish applying the changes going to the position of where you started the rename with <strong class=\" \">Enter</strong> (or just cancel it with <strong class=\" \">ESC</strong>).    </p>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083060\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"PyDev Rename Occurrences"});